Subject: [PATCH] ui: calm address bar — centered, minimal, fades on scroll

Patches the OmniboxView and LocationBarView to implement Fennec's calm
address bar:
  - Centered in the toolbar (not left-aligned)
  - Minimum width 480px; expands to 680px on focus (CSS transition)
  - Pill-shaped border radius (--fnc-radius-pill)
  - Entire browser chrome fades to 0 opacity at full scroll depth;
    restores on any mouse movement (uses ScrollObserver)

All widths and transitions are driven by CSS tokens so Mods can
override them without C++ changes.

TODO: Stub. Full implementation in Phase 2.
      Tracked: fennec-browser/fennec#12

PILLAR: Calm UI
JOURNAL: none
